  </ul>

  <h2>Looking Forward</h2>
  <p>
    Minimal UX design isn't a trend – it's a timeless approach that respects
    users' time and cognitive load. As technology becomes more complex, our
    interfaces should become more intuitive.
  </p>

  <p>
    The future belongs to designs that fade into the background, allowing users
    to focus on what truly matters: accomplishing their goals with joy and
    efficiency.
